    "title": "Hiding and Resistance",
    "explanation": "Avril se cache dans le labo. — notice se cache: the se makes the verb reflexive. She hides HERSELF.\n\nOn a privé les savants de tout. — privé de means deprived OF. The de connects privé to what was taken.\n\nRe-read and find every se + [verb]. Who acts upon themselves? Then find de after verbs — what follows?"
